::DrillBit::

DrillBit walked to where KitKat and Phobia are.
"Hey, you looked really down, so I came to cheer you up." He said to
KitKat.

::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod walked out of the brig, and outside the Ark. He saw that the Ark
was in pretty bad shape. It would have to be tottaly rebuilt, in order
to keep history in tackt. And the Autobots would have to be found. He
decided to stay, incase of another attack.
